content:
next one is "Altar in the sun": Blood in, blood out
Locked in till I’m living in a box
But how else does anyone leave?

I love when things that used to hurt 
just turn me on
You can find me at my altar in the sun
Ready to risk it all!

I got it a feeling that it’s coming and it’s coming fast
I got it a feeling that it’s coming, coming

Time drips
in an hourglass, shaking its
hips 
Imma send something better than
this
aahhhh

I love when things that used to hurt 
just turn me on
You can find me at my altar in the sun
if we make it through the night.

I got it a feeling that it’s coming and it’s coming fast
I got it a feeling that it’s coming, coming
